OL,3,CFares across Transport for Wales up by
OL,4,Can average of 4.6%
OL,6,FPassengers across Wales will see
OL,7,Fregulated rail fares rise by up to 6%
OL,8,Ffrom Sunday 2nd March, following a
OL,9,Fdecision made by the Welsh Government.
OL,11,FTransport for Wales' Anytime Day
OL,12,FSingle fares will increase by 3%, 7-
OL,13,FDay Season ticket fares will increase
OL,14,Fby 3.5%, and Anytime Day Return fares
OL,15,Fand Off Peak Return fares will both
OL,16,Fincrease by 6%.
