OL,3,CFares across Transport for Wales up by
OL,4,Can average of 4.6%
OL,6,FCommenting on the changes the Welsh
OL,7,FConservative Shadow Cabinet Secretary
OL,8,Ffor Transport, Peter Fox MS said the
OL,9,FWelsh Government need to ensure
OL,10,Fservices are improving "so that hard
OL,11,Fworking commuters get what they
OL,12,Fdeserve."
OL,14,FHe said: "Passengers across the Core
OL,15,FValley Lines have faced severe
OL,16,Fdisruption and the works are still
OL,17,Fongoing. It's no wonder passengers
OL,18,Fwill question these increases whilst
OL,19,Fpatiently awaiting the works being
OL,20,Ffinished.
