OL,6,F"People want value for money, and
OL,7,Funtil significant service improvements
OL,8,Fare delivered across Wales, passengers
OL,9,Fwill continue to question the hundreds
OL,10,Fof millions of pounds Labour has spent
OL,11,Fon TfW, alongside the rising cost of
OL,12,Fpassenger fares."
OL,14,FIn a statement, Transport for Wales
OL,15,Fsaid: "As a not-for-profit
